                    <h3>About</h3>
	                <p>
	                    This bundle integrates the functionnalities of the responsive framework Foundation, from Zurb (thanks guys), into Symfony2 by providing templates, Twig extensions, services and commands. You can quickly setup a responsive theme for an interface for your projet. It will have the "look'n'feel", the responsiveness and the simplicity of Foundation.<br />
                        <b>BE AWARE: THIS BUNDLE WILL NOT ADD THE FOUNDATION FRAMEWORK BUT RATHER FUNCTIONNALITIES FOR SYMFONY TO WORK WITH IT</b><br />
                        To include Foundation, jQuery, Normalize & Modernizer you can use the CloudFlare CDN. This bundle uses icons from Font Awesome. To add it, you can use the bootstrapcdn.
                    </p>
